FT  23 MAR 93 / UK Company News: Sharpe &amp; Fisher ahead to Pounds 1.5m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
SHARPE &amp; Fisher, the building supplies and property group, returned profits
of Pounds 1.45m pre-tax for 1992, a sharp improvement on the previous year's
restated Pounds 452,000.
The shares responded with a 12p rise to 95p.
