1.49m - comparable figures here were been restated to conform with FRS 3.
Overall turnover edged ahead from Pounds 43.8m to Pounds 45.3m.
An unchanged final dividend of 2.5p holds the total at 4p from earnings more
than doubled at 7.8p (3.5p). Year-end borrowings were reduced from Pounds 7m
to Pounds 6.5m.
