continue to focus on the provincial insurance market. The current hardening
of rates in the insurance market and our selective underwriting policy
provide us with every opportunity to develop our business successfully.'
Mr Laing added that an independent chairman was presently being sought. Two
non-executive directors are also to be appointed, one of which is to be a
nominee for Electra Kingsway, the lead investor in the venture.
Other institutional investors include Phoenix Development Capital Fund, Bank
of Boston and Brown Shipley Venture Managers.
